<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>login</title>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/register-login.css">
  <style>
    select, span{
      margin: 0 ;
      padding: 0;
    }
    select {
      height: 20px;
      width: 56%;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      margin-left:3px;
      font-size: .8em;
    }
    .user-type {
      margin-left: 2em;
      border: 1px solid #aaa;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius:  5px;
      background: #eee;
      padding-bottom: .35em;
    }
    #register-instruction {
      margin-top: 3em;
      font-size: .8em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main">
        <img src="images/user.png" id="user-head">
        <div id="container">
          <h3>用户登录</h3><a href="register.html" class="login">注册</a><hr>
            <form class="register-form" method="post" action="index.html">
              选择用户类型:
              <span class="user-type"><select >
                <option value="学生">学生</option>
                <option value="教师">教师</option>
                <option value="领导">领导</option>
                <option value="管理员">管理员</option>
              </select></span><br>
              <label for="username">用户名：</label><input type="text" id="username"><br>
              <label for="password">输入密码：</label><input type="password" id="password"><br>
              <label for="password">确认密码：</label><input type="password" id="password"><br>
              <input type="reset" id="reset" value="重置"><input type="submit" id="submit" value="提交">
            </form>
          <p id="register-instruction">关于登录，若您是领导、教师或学生且已有分配账号，请直接以此账号登录，若尚未知账号，请与管理员联系。家长请先注册再登录。</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>